OL,5, Cadbury has shrunk the size of its     
OL,6, Dairy Milk sharing bars by 10%, but    
OL,7, will not reduce the price for          
OL,8, customers.                             
OL,10,FParent company Mondelez blamed costs   
OL,11,Fassociated with the production of its  
OL,12,Fchocolate spiking, as it reduced the   
OL,13,Fbars' size from 200g to 180g.          
OL,15,FThey are still typically being sold at 
OL,16,F#2 despite the downsize.               
OL,18,FUS firm Mondelez said the move was the 
OL,19,Ffirst for that size of Dairy Milk bar  
OL,20,Fin a decade.                           
